Cell["\<\
This gives the Schmidt decomposition. The first list stores the Schmidt \
numbers and the rest lists store the corresponding vectors in the first and \
second part of the total tensor-product space.\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->1542106748,ExpressionUUID->"2240f3e3-6c75-435e-845f-d8b89c32675e"],

