Cell["\<\
As the vector in question is separable, the Schmidt rank must be 1 -- there \
is only one non-zero Schmidt number.\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->1619579837,ExpressionUUID->"f62078e8-6d1c-41c8-8c9c-b4f1dcad6886"],

